title: Graduate Gets Illegal Injections at Party, Butt Grows to 59 Inches (VIDEO)
text:
February 15, 2017 by Alissa Kombert 0 Shares Advertisement 
Ain't no party like a... butt injection party? Economics graduate Courtney Barnes took drastic measures six years ago to get the backside she wanted. Only she may have gone overboard. A post shared by MsMiami (@damn_msmiami) on Jan 12, 2017 at 7:47pm PST 
The Miami resident underwent three rounds of illegal injections at "pumping parties." And now her backside measures 59 inches! The 32-year-old has turned her assets into a business, sharing lots of photos on social media with her 400K+ followers. A post shared by MsMiami (@damn_msmiami) on Jan 24, 2017 at 7:45pm PST 
But the added attention may be more than she wanted. Now she's looking into a reduction, as she feels it's difficult for people to take her seriously. 
She goes on to explain how she was naive at the time and doesn't recommend the illegal enhancements. Watch the video above for more on Courtney's story! Advertisement
